The,Amper,Music,API,allows,developers,to,programmatically,create,and,download,audio,projects,with,the,Amper,Music,system,Amper,is,an,AI,composer,performer,and,producer,that,allows,users,to,create,and,customize,original,music,for,their,content,Users,can,select,the,desired,mood,style,and,length,of,the,piece,and,then,customize,it,further,using,the,editing,functionality